Text: I appreciate the effort, but you should really upload lossless stuff in FLAC and not zipped/rared/7zipped, because people won't seed as much if they have to keep two versions on their PC (one packed and one unpacked).
Im kinda glad that its in the wma form, it may not be as high quality or anything but its easier to get on a music player to play it, personally i think great effort and stuff, good job
